rmacher" title="Friedrich Schleiermacher">Friedrich Schleiermacher</a></span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Louis_Segond" title="Louis Segond">Louis Segond</a></span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/David_Strauss" title="David Strauss">David Strauss</a></span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ernst_Troeltsch" title="Ernst Troeltsch">Ernst Troeltsch</a></span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Samuel_Vincent" title="Samuel Vincent">Samuel Vincent</a></span></td>
